<div class='demo-title'>
  Dialog
</div>
<div class='demo-card demo-card--list'>
  <MaterialList as |Item Divider|>
    <Item as |item|>
      Show dialogs in fullscreen
      <item.switch
        @checked={{this.fullscreen}}
        @onChange={{fn this.update 'fullscreen'}}
      />
    </Item>
    <Divider />
    <MaterialDialog @fullscreen={{this.fullscreen}}>
      <:trigger as |open|>
        <Item {{on 'click' open}}>
          Alert
        </Item>
      </:trigger>
      <:dialog as |item close|>
        <item.content>
          <p>
            To cross the river, you've to answer these questions three!
          </p>
        </item.content>
        <item.footer as |Button|>
          <Button @unelevated={{true}} {{on 'click' close}}>
            OK
          </Button>
        </item.footer>
      </:dialog>
    </MaterialDialog>
    <MaterialDialog @fullscreen={{this.fullscreen}}>
      <:trigger as |open|>
        <Item {{on 'click' open}}>
          Simple
        </Item>
      </:trigger>
      <:dialog as |item|>
        <item.header>
          Select your account
        </item.header>
        <item.content>
          <MaterialList @avatar={{true}} as |Item|>
            <Item as |item|>
              <item.icon @leading={{true}}>
                person
              </item.icon>
              sir_lancelot_the_brave@example.com
            </Item>
            <Item as |item|>
              <item.icon @leading={{true}}>
                person
              </item.icon>
              sir_bedevere_the_wise@example.com
            </Item>
            <Item as |item|>
              <item.icon @leading={{true}}>
                person
              </item.icon>
              sir_galahad_the_pure@example.com
            </Item>
            <Item as |item|>
              <item.icon @leading={{true}}>
                add
              </item.icon>
              Add an account
            </Item>
          </MaterialList>
        </item.content>
      </:dialog>
    </MaterialDialog>
    <MaterialDialog @fullscreen={{this.fullscreen}}>
      <:trigger as |open|>
        <Item {{on 'click' open}}>
          confirmation
        </Item>
      </:trigger>
      <:dialog as |item close|>
        <item.header>
          How brave is Sir Robin?
        </item.header>
        <item.content>
          <MaterialList @avatar={{true}} as |Item|>
            <Item as |item|>
              <item.radioButton @leading={{true}} />
              Very brave
            </Item>
            <Item as |item|>
              <item.radioButton @leading={{true}} />
              Not quite so brave as Sir Lancelot
            </Item>
            <Item as |item|>
              <item.radioButton @leading={{true}} />
              Not brave
            </Item>
          </MaterialList>
        </item.content>
        <item.footer as |Button|>
          <Button {{on 'click' close}}>
            abort
          </Button>
          <Button @unelevated={{true}} {{on 'click' close}}>
            Confirm
          </Button>
        </item.footer>
      </:dialog>
    </MaterialDialog>
    <MaterialDialog @fullscreen={{this.fullscreen}} @scrollable={{true}}>
      <:trigger as |open|>
        <Item {{on 'click' open}}>
          Scrollable
        </Item>
      </:trigger>
      <:dialog as |item close|>
        <item.header>
          How to use the Holy Hand Grenade
        </item.header>
        <item.content>
          <p>
            {{#let
              'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Morbi
            maximus tellus id dictum lobortis. Nunc sit amet hendrerit neque,
            eget efficitur enim. Duis consectetur, sem eget tempus pulvinar,
            diam risus placerat augue, ut scelerisque nibh purus quis lacus.
            Suspendisse accumsan mi et aliquet ultrices. Quisque malesuada
            rutrum nunc et commodo. Donec a mauris pulvinar, interdum elit nec,
            placerat tortor. Nulla dictum tristique enim eu cursus. Etiam at
            velit ut metus faucibus sollicitudin id non eros. In sit amet est
            vitae sapien scelerisque elementum sit amet ac libero. Fusce
            porttitor tincidunt augue, nec consequat nisl luctus a. Nunc in
            imperdiet nulla. Donec a fermentum mauris, imperdiet tempus lorem.
            Praesent eu odio sed felis ultrices consectetur. Etiam auctor quis
            mauris quis tincidunt. Vivamus aliquam non nulla et malesuada. Nam
            cursus orci id quam cursus, a tempus arcu posuere.'
              as |lorem|
            }}
              Remove the pin and count till three. Three should be the number
              you count and the third number you've counted should be three. Not
              two, not four. Five is right out! Then you sit amet, consectetur
              adipiscing elit. Morbi maximus tellus id dictum lobortis. Nunc sit
